title: Photos: Caleb Evans scores five total touchdowns in Bishop Dunne's 35-14 win over Argyle Liberty Christian
text: Bishop Dunne senior quarterback Caleb Evans (6) out runs Argyle Liberty Christian senior linebacker Nick Horton (10) for positive yards before being stopped, during the first half of a Friday night high school football game, on Oct. 16, 2015 at Bishop Dunne Catholic high school in Dallas. Ben Torres/Special Contributor
